body:
# CodeCamp2015

Seattle Code Camp 2015: September 12th, 2015 at Seattle University's Pigott Building

Thanks for checking out the materials for my Seattle Code Camp 2015 presentation, ["Their Exits and Their Entrances: Actors in the .NET Framework"](https://seattle.codecamp.us/Session/Details/68) Prior to Code Camp, I will upload the slides, my script, and the code samples I'll be using. After Code Camp, I'll try to capture any differences between the 'as-prepared' materials and how things actually went.

Thanks again,

Carter
